# Product (FridgeWise / TrueSight)

Canonical product docs: **`docs/product/`** (`@docs/product/roadmap.md`, `domain-model.md`, `user-stories.md`).

When roadmap or scope changes, update `docs/product/` first, then `.awp-workspace/1-design/ROADMAP.yaml` and related registers.

## Problem

Users don't know what's in their fridge. Perishables expire before they're used.

## Solution

Log inventory → recipe suggestions from available ingredients → deduct inventory on recipe acceptance.

## Versions

- V1: Manual inventory + recipe suggestions
- V2: Camera-based fridge scanning

## Design constraint

Fully usable on mobile and desktop.
